{"tid":1653488,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講左咁耐仲有好多人未裝保命Parachute !! 真係救你一命","createTime":"2019-10-14T05:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T07:06:24.000Z","uid":28020,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"523046a45b524765b17663d7d03485452cf8b3df","tid":1653488,"uid":28020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:55:33.000Z","msg":"一早set好語音siri指令<br />\n<br />\n「開parachute」<br />\n<br />\n或者apple watch 開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俾狗咬緊急果陣語音叫siri開<br />\n個app就會自動幫你求救<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">定位<br />\n開live<br />\n錄影<br />\nSend 求救msg</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong>係定位呀!!!<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span></strong></strong></span><br />\n咁多手足失蹤就係唔會去左邊<br />\n佢會track 你位置Send出去嫁!!!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/09/02/parachute%E7%82%BA%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%B1%82%E6%95%91-%E9%81%8B%E7%94%A8add-on%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9%E6%9B%B4%E8%BF%85%E9%80%9F/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2Fparachute%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2595%2591-%25E9%2581%258B%25E7%2594%25A8add-on%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%259B%25B4%25E8%25BF%2585%25E9%2580%259F%2Famp%2F&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAqFdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=69bb4a04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/09/02/parachute%E7%82%BA%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%B1%82%E6%95%91-%E9%81%8B%E7%94%A8add-on%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9%E6%9B%B4%E8%BF%85%E9%80%9F/amp/</a><br />\n《 Parachute 》是 iOS 上的求生手機，用戶在危急狀況下需要求救時，只需按著程式畫面一秒以上就會向事先設定好的聯絡人發出求救短訊，同時會啟動鏡頭和收音咪錄下證據。聯絡人不單可以收到信息，還會收到求救者的即時串流影像、地圖位置和最近聯絡紀錄等，讓他決定下一步行動，例如立即趕往迎救。<br />\n<br />\n由於如果手機開著直播畫面很可能會刺激穿制服的兇徒作更激烈的行動，所以《 Parachute 》啟動求救時不會有聲響，畫面也會是漆黑一片的，需要緊按畫面上的眼睛圖示時才會看到錄影畫面和求救狀況等資料，要結束求救就要同時按著眼睛和「 X 」圖示。"},{"pid":"85749b8e47b26c6351d49d33d8c5d93514a5b92f","tid":1653488,"uid":28020,"like":0,"disl